==Hindi==
===Etymology===
From Sanskrit [[धन्य]], auspicious, blessed, lucky and [[वाद]], speech

===Noun===
'''धन्यवाद''' (dhanyavād)
#[[thank you]]
#[[benediction]]
#[[gratitude]]
#[[acknowledgment]]

